WITH RankedSuppliers AS (
    SELECT s.s_suppkey, s.s_name, SUM(ps.ps_supplycost * ps.ps_availqty) AS total_supply_value
    FROM supplier s
    JOIN partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    GROUP BY s.s_suppkey, s.s_name
), HighValueOrders AS (
    SELECT o.o_orderkey, o.o_totalprice, c.c_name
    FROM orders o
    JOIN customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
    WHERE o.o_totalprice > (SELECT AVG(o_totalprice) FROM orders)
), OrderLineInfo AS (
    SELECT l.l_orderkey, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_line_value
    FROM lineitem l
    GROUP BY l.l_orderkey
), FinalReport AS (
    SELECT hv.o_orderkey, hv.o_totalprice, hv.c_name, rs.s_name, rs.total_supply_value, oli.total_line_value
    FROM HighValueOrders hv
    JOIN RankedSuppliers rs ON hv.o_orderkey = rs.s_suppkey
    JOIN OrderLineInfo oli ON hv.o_orderkey = oli.l_orderkey
)
SELECT o.o_orderkey, o.o_totalprice, o.c_name, s.s_name, s.total_supply_value, li.total_line_value
FROM FinalReport o
JOIN RankedSuppliers s ON o.s_name = s.s_name
JOIN OrderLineInfo li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
WHERE s.total_supply_value > 100000
ORDER BY o.o_totalprice DESC, s.total_supply_value ASC
LIMIT 50

INNER JOIN ("customer" INNER JOIN "orders" AS "orders0" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "orders0"."o_custkey") ON "t7"."EXPR$0" < "orders0"."o_totalprice") AS "t8" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t8"."O_ORDERKEY" = "s1"."L_ORDERKEY") ON "t6"."S_SUPPKEY" = "t8"."O_ORDERKEY") AS "t9" ON "t4"."S_NAME" = "t9"."S_NAME"
INNER JOIN "s1" AS "s10" ON "t9"."O_ORDERKEY" = "s10"."L_ORDERKEY"
ORDER BY "t9"."O_TOTALPRICE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t4"."TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE"
LIMIT 50) AS "t11"

SELECT COALESCE("l_orderkey", "l_orderkey") AS "L_ORDERKEY", "l_extendedprice" * (1 - "l_discount") AS "FD_COL_1"
FROM "lineitem"

SELECT COALESCE("t12"."O_ORDERKEY", "t12"."O_ORDERKEY") AS "O_ORDERKEY", "t12"."O_TOTALPRICE", "t12"."C_NAME", "t12"."S_NAME", "t12"."TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE", "t12"."TOTAL_LINE_VALUE"
FROM (SELECT "t9"."O_ORDERKEY", "t9"."O_TOTALPRICE", "t9"."C_NAME", "t3"."S_NAME", "t3"."TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE", "t10"."TOTAL_LINE_VALUE"
FROM (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", SUM("partsupp"."ps_supplycost" * "partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name"
HAVING SUM("partsupp"."ps_supplycost" * "partsupp"."ps_availqty") > 100000.00) AS "t3"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "t7"."O_ORDERKEY", "t7"."O_TOTALPRICE", "t7"."C_NAME", "t5"."S_NAME", "t5"."TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE", "t8"."TOTAL_LINE_VALUE"
FROM (SELECT "supplier0"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier0"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", SUM("partsupp0"."ps_supplycost" * "partsupp0"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE"
FROM "supplier" AS "supplier0"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" AS "partsupp0" ON "supplier0"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp0"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier0"."s_suppkey", "supplier0"."s_name") AS "t5"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "orders0"."o_orderkey" AS "O_ORDERKEY", "orders0"."o_totalprice" AS "O_TOTALPRICE", "customer"."c_name" AS "C_NAME"
FROM (SELECT AVG("o_totalprice") AS "EXPR$0"
FROM "orders") AS "t6"
INNER JOIN ("customer" INNER JOIN "orders" AS "orders0" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "orders0"."o_custkey") ON "t6"."EXPR$0" < "orders0"."o_totalprice") AS "t7" INNER JOIN (SELECT "L_ORDERKEY", SUM("FD_COL_1") AS "TOTAL_LINE_VALUE"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "L_ORDERKEY") AS "t8" ON "t7"."O_ORDERKEY" = "t8"."L_ORDERKEY") ON "t5"."S_SUPPKEY" = "t7"."O_ORDERKEY") AS "t9" ON "t3"."S_NAME" = "t9"."S_NAME"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "L_ORDERKEY", SUM("FD_COL_1") AS "TOTAL_LINE_VALUE"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "L_ORDERKEY") AS "t10" ON "t9"."O_ORDERKEY" = "t10"."L_ORDERKEY"
ORDER BY "t9"."O_TOTALPRICE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE"
LIMIT 50) AS "t12"
